king for intruders. No \none can escape our sense of smell.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":0,"max":0},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":1},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""},"threat":{"rank":"Medium 5","impulse":"","oppositionLevel":5}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557629804,"modifiedTime":1781557629804,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"KWoLr1i1hSqmDhNk","name":"William the Man of Law","type":"threat","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","items":[{"_id":"wDWrLo0TzhXzdnzH","name":"William the Man of Law - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a prominent lawyer and I know all of \nBardolf ’s secrets. I manage the accounts of both the Factories \nand mine with zealous attention.\nBardolf’s personal \nguard</p>","notes":"The City of Pigs - bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 206.","positive":"I am a prominent lawyer and I know all of \nBardolf ’s secrets. I manage the accounts of both the Factories \nand mine with zealous attention.\nBardolf’s personal \nguard","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557623800,"modifiedTime":1781557623800,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"C3DU9ltsDxY1b3oI","name":"Source Text","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>– Minor NPC (1 Wound)\nDescriptor: I am a prominent lawyer and I know all of \nBardolf ’s secrets. I manage the accounts of both the Factories \nand mine with zealous attention.\nBardolf’s personal \nguard</p>","notes":"The City of Pigs - bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 206."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557623800,"modifiedTime":1781557623800,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"scenarioActorSlug":"core-book-city-of-pigs-william-the-man-of-law-206","collection":"Core Book","adventureSlug":"city-of-pigs","adventureTitle":"The City of Pigs","sourceFile":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf","page":206,"role":"Minor NPC"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"The City of Pigs","origin":"Core Book","role":"Minor NPC","notes":"<p>– Minor NPC (1 Wound)\nDescriptor: I am a prominent lawyer and I know all of \nBardolf ’s secrets. I manage the accounts of both the Factories \nand mine with zealous attention.\nBardolf’s personal \nguard</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":0,"max":0},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":1},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""},"threat":{"rank":"Medium 5","impulse":"","oppositionLevel":5}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557623800,"modifiedTime":1781557623800,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"KexEaEQYxcpZa8h3","name":"Gerard Dubois the Incapable Noble","type":"threat","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","items":[{"_id":"8ZbNVovdGRDxXyTw","name":"Gerard Dubois the Incapable Noble - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am the noble baron of Durfort and my \nword is law. I live in the shadow of my late father’s glory.</p>","notes":"Red-hood / Iskra - bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 122.","positive":"I am the noble baron of Durfort and my \nword is law. I live in the shadow of my late father’s glory.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557621314,"modifiedTime":1781557621314,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"CTzZYzQyPH9Xv6y2","name":"Source Text","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>– Minor NPC (1 Wound)\nDescriptor: I am the noble baron of Durfort and my \nword is law. I live in the shadow of my late father’s glory.\nAgenda: Put an end to the menacing werewolves and \ncover up any possible mischief.\nElizaveta – The cruel bride</p>","notes":"Red-hood / Iskra - bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 122."},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557621314,"modifiedTime":1781557621314,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"scenarioActorSlug":"core-book-red-hood-iskra-gerard-dubois-the-incapable-noble-122","collection":"Core Book","adventureSlug":"red-hood-iskra","adventureTitle":"Red-hood 